   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Email Thread Summarizer\\n\",\"**NLP Project 44 of 100** — Condense long email chains into key decisions, action items, and participants.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Parse email thread structure (From, Date, Body).\\n\",\"2. Extract key decisions and action items.\\n\",\"3. Generate concise thread summaries.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, re, requests\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nSEED = 42\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"EMAIL_THREAD = [\\n    {'from':'alice@co.com','date':'2025-03-01 09:00','body':'Hi team, we need to finalize the Q2 budget by Friday. Please review the attached spreadsheet and share your department estimates.'},\\n    {'from':'bob@co.com','date':'2025-03-01 10:30','body':'Thanks Alice. Marketing budget is $45K. I will send the breakdown by EOD.'},\\n    {'from':'carol@co.com','date':'2025-03-01 11:15','body':'Engineering needs $120K for the new infrastructure migration. This is non-negotiable.'},\\n    {'from':'alice@co.com','date':'2025-03-01 14:00','body':'Got it. Carol, can you provide a phased breakdown? Bob, please include the conference costs.'},\\n    {'from':'bob@co.com','date':'2025-03-02 09:00','body':'Updated marketing budget: $45K base + $10K for the annual conference = $55K total.'},\\n    {'from':'carol@co.com','date':'2025-03-02 11:00','body':'Phase 1 (April): $50K for cloud setup. Phase 2 (May): $40K for migration. Phase 3 (June): $30K for testing. Total: $120K.'},\\n    {'from':'alice@co.com','date':'2025-03-02 15:00','body':'Perfect. Total Q2 budget: Marketing $55K + Engineering $120K = $175K. I will submit to finance. Meeting Friday at 2pm to finalize.'},\\n]\\n\\nfor e in EMAIL_THREAD:\\n    print(f'From: {e[\\\"from\\\"]} | {e[\\\"date\\\"]}')\\n    print(f'  {e[\\\"body\\\"][:80]}...')\\n    print()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Extractive Summary\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"def summarize_thread(emails):\\n    participants = list(set(e['from'] for e in emails))\\n    # Extract numbers/decisions\\n    decisions = []\\n    action_items = []\\n    for e in emails:\\n        body = e['body']\\n        if any(w in body.lower() for w in ['total','final','submit','decision','approved']):\\n            decisions.append(body)\\n        if any(w in body.lower() for w in ['need to','please','will send','can you','meeting']):\\n            action_items.append(f\\\"{e['from'].split('@')[0]}: {body[:80]}\\\")\\n    \\n    summary = f\\\"\\\"\\\"THREAD SUMMARY\\n==============\\nParticipants: {', '.join(p.split('@')[0] for p in participants)}\\nEmails: {len(emails)}\\nDate range: {emails[0]['date']} to {emails[-1]['date']}\\n\\nKEY DECISIONS:\\n{chr(10).join('• ' + d[:100] for d in decisions[:3])}\\n\\nACTION ITEMS:\\n{chr(10).join('• ' + a for a in action_items[:5])}\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    return summary\\n\\nprint(summarize_thread(EMAIL_THREAD))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## LLM-Based Summary\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"thread_text = '\\\\n'.join(f\\\"From: {e['from']} ({e['date']}): {e['body']}\\\" for e in EMAIL_THREAD)\\nprompt = f\\\"Summarize this email thread into: 1) Key decisions, 2) Action items, 3) Next steps. Be concise.\\\\n\\\\n{thread_text} /no_think\\\"\\ntry:\\n    r = requests.post('http://localhost:11434/api/generate',json={'model':'qwen3:1.7b','prompt':prompt,'stream':False},timeout=60)\\n    print(r.json().get('response','No response'))\\nexcept: print('Ollama unavailable. Use extractive summary above.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Email thread summarization extracts decisions and action items** from long chains.\\n\",\"- **Rule-based extraction catches explicit keywords** (total, meeting, please).\\n\",\"- **LLMs produce more natural summaries** with better context understanding.\\n\",\"- **For production, integrate with email APIs** (Gmail, Outlook) for automatic processing.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
    " \"metadata\":{\"kernelspec\":{\"display_name\":\"Python 3\",\"language\":\"python\",\"name\":\"python3\"},\"language_info\":{\"name\":\"python\",\"version\":\"3.11.0\"}},\n",
    " \"nbformat\":4,\"nbformat_minor\":5\n",
    "}\n"
